e":"2019-08-29T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"邊讀"},{"pid":"62df5bbc871ae62a28371de51026915cf5620b4d","tid":1516262,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a410784693bdc78d24b59173599838f68c3dc5","tid":1516262,"uid":283712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:14:23.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山中心無人應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35eb1f4efd955fdb8e74997ff20f93621c1b9210","tid":1516262,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:17:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd66891c645ad9ba54707544469670cbaf36f845","tid":1516262,"uid":283712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44a410784693bdc78d24b59173599838f68c3dc5","tid":1516262,"uid":283712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:14:23.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山中心無人應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:22:57.000Z","msg":"有人應啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb9da3e6321d169dce7040c5700400443b1dd3f","tid":1516262,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:24:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>反欺凌<br />\n保護警察兒女 你我有責</strong></span><br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n各位中小學生 為左反欺凌 保護警察兒女<br />\n如果有確鑿證據證明邊位同學老豆老母係警察既話記得要<br />\n1.搵人放佢大頭相上黎<br />\n2.寫埋住邊區<br />\n3.寫埋讀咩學校<br />\n等市民可以隨時留意住佢地有冇比人欺凌 係有需要既時候可以保護佢地<br />\n<br />\n因為欺凌係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔局限係校園</span></span>架<br />\n而家市民咁仇警 有人可能會作出自然反應係街上做小動作搞警察兒女<br />\n例如:<br />\n1.唔小心撞佢出馬路<br />\n2.警察兒衝紅燈個陣唔小心女擋住佢唔比佢上行人路<br />\n3.唔小心踼/撞佢落樓梯<br />\n4.係街拍蚊個陣唔小心打中佢<br />\n5.係巴士唔小心擋住佢唔比佢落車<br />\n6.係巴士/小巴唔小心唔讓開比佢入去靠窗位坐<br />\n7.係巴士/小巴唔小心唔讓開比佢離開個靠窗位<br />\n8.係行人路/過馬路個陣唔小心&quot;KICK&quot;跌佢<br />\n9.唔小心擋住LIP口唔比佢入升降機<br />\n10.警察兒女趕返學搭LIP個陣 唔小心撳哂咁多層<br />\n11.係佢要上車/追車個陣唔小心扮健身撚當街捉住佢扮SALE野唔比佢走 <br />\n12.係街上唔小心撞佢落花槽<br />\n13.唔小心撞佢部手機落地<br />\n14.唔小心撞佢手上拎住既其他野落地<br />\n15.唔小心倒瀉野食/野飲落佢地件校服到<br />\n16.唔小心倒瀉野食/野飲「入」佢地個書包到<br />\n17.係鋪頭入面唔小心放左啲未比錢既野入佢個袋到<br />\n18.係佢行過個陣唔小心屋企倒屎水/污糟水落樓<br />\n19.唔小心打開佢書包拉鍊 等佢啲野跌哂出黎<br />\n20.唔小心放啲蛇蟲鼠蟻入佢書包 <br />\nETC.<br />\n<br />\n大家見到有人咁人既話記得要保護佢地 就算啲警察兒女幾忙幾趕時間都要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉住佢地</span></span>幫佢地報警 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比佢地走</span></span><br />\n你地知香港警察做野幾有效率架啦 一個人日日等幾次39分鐘<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都唔係好嘥時間姐</span></span><br />\n如果佢地自己打電話想搵人幫手 千祈唔好唔小心轟佢部手機落地然後踢到母雷公咁遠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1516112/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1516112/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1516100/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1516100/page/1?post=2</a>"},{"pid":"83d2d3f8070e267bd02648ee186ee37ddf3f4412","tid":1516262,"uid":231818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"7217057f77235ca2b529cc654f164207e3cb395b","tid":1516262,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"喺恆耀安馬路嗌嗌到去耀安球場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望你地聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb3ae3911cbf2bb4249fdf3ad7217eb5887c338","tid":1516262,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35922847f24f680b059fa705d128bf9c926428c7","tid":1516262,"uid":288106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:10:22.000Z","msg":"無人回應我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"你係咪岩先叫完香港果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a77777d83ea620c91289887cb34137b534aaa4f","tid":1516262,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"約定大家今晚嗌！！！"},{"pid":"59176aed432b8d4477cf9aa66f7e6c9e6f535cbc","tid":1516262,"uid":311807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:06:50.000Z","msg":"好 約定10點嗌"},{"pid":"3cee6414e22776a1452bf6cc203fe2db3da65005","tid":1516262,"uid":175143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"準備啦"}]}